    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-dark mb-4">Types of Capstone Assignments Offered by Professionals</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">There are several types of capstone assignments. They come in different forms, with a wide range of activities, lengths, and weightings. This section will help you understand different capstone assignments help you can get from experts today.</p>
    </section>
    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-dark mb-4">Externally-oriented Capstone Assignment</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Externally-oriented Capstone Assignment is a popular type of capstone task. When undertaking a project of this nature, students engage in a professionally oriented assignment to develop a solution for a scenario or problem.</p>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">You must work towards a solution in outlined stages, collecting data, analyzing the collected information, making decisions, and developing an outcome. You need to combine behaviors, processes, and products in the case of the study.</p>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">When undertaking these assignments, students need to come up with reports and presentations.</p>
    </section>
    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-dark mb-4">Practice-oriented simulations</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Practice-oriented simulations cut across all courses of study. They are popular in media, science, and business courses. Similar to consultancies, these simulations recreate the context and professional fields' state, allowing you to experience the pressures, challenges, and issues related to the career.</p>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">These capstones are complex and holistic. They continue for a reasonable period. Students need to take on responsibility allowing them to experience their future fields of practice. They gain skills in maters planning and management of daily activities.</p>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Practice-oriented is relatively expensive to set up and sustain. They require intensive support from staff and non-standard delivery, and they can be incorporated into the normal timetable.</p>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">In practical-oriented capstones, you are assessed based on the simulation activity's evidence with a general combination of evidence relating to behaviors, processes, and results.</p>
    </section>
    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-dark mb-4">Task-oriented simulations</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Task-oriented is paper-based or online simulations. In this type of capstone project, you are not compelled to capture the entire field of study. You instead need to focus on a set of defined activities with several aims. They are common in business courses.</p>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">They tend to manage the activities highly; therefore, you need to be careful when doing a task-oriented capstone. These assignment types provide you with the scope and extensive complexity to enable you to put it into practice, develop and transfer various attributes and skills required in a capstone experience and as a qualified student.</p>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Deliverables most focus on a series of personal reflections, achieving the simulation goals without forgetting behavioral and performance competencies.</p>
    </section>
    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-dark mb-4">Academic Inquiry Capstone Assignment</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Another common type of capstone assignment across all disciplines. They may operate as an academic or personal inquiry experience or as a research apprenticeship. Here, students can pick topics and technics of inquiry from reflective activities to formal research or span creative.</p>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">If your study involves collecting human data, you need to use secondary data as opposed to primary data. Students carry out defined inquiries and develop a result as appropriate to the area of study.</p>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Assignment deliverables cut across reports, presentation lecture to fellow students, and creative works.</p>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-dark mb-3 mt-6">Placements</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Placements commonly feature in the final year of course study in selected courses. They particularly prevalent in health courses. It is important to note that not all placements meet the capstone assignment framework.</p>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">However, capstone placements usually stress critical awareness and active learning as well as integration practice knowledge. They often involve an element of supported academic study.</p>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Students engage in a critical inquiry or academic activity alongside their practice and seek to integrate and resolve conceptual, theoretical, and practical elements of their field.</p>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Placements commonly require you to extensively focus your efforts on reflecting on your abilities and progressive development requirements. The assessment focuses on the precise nature and balance of activities while involving reflective reports combining workplace competencies with short integrative writing pieces.</p>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-dark mb-3 mt-6">Practice-based consultancies</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Finally, Practice-based consultancies are also popular across most disciplines. From creative arts, business to health disciplines, students are expected to write a capstone project. You must extensively recreate the context and state of the subject of study; you will get exposed to challenges and pressure related to the real-world field and probably your future career.</p>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">These capstones are complex and holistic. They continuously proceed for a significant period, requiring regular management of the human resource. Furthermore, the practice-based consultancy has project-based features.  Assessment evidence combines behaviors, processes, results. It is critical to note that there is little focus on the results as requirements may vary extensively depending on the study's course.</p>
